Package: orbbec-lidar-sdk
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Orbbec LiDAR SDK runtime library
 This package provides the runtime library for integrating and utilizing
 Orbbec LiDAR devices, currently supporting single-line lidar.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: orbbec-lidar-sdk-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: orbbec-lidar-sdk (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Orbbec LiDAR SDK development files
 This package provides the development files (headers and CMake configuration)
 for building applications that use the Orbbec LiDAR SDK.
 .
 This package contains the header files and CMake configuration files needed
 to compile and link applications against the Orbbec LiDAR SDK.


